.SH NOTES
.sp
.LP
The ISP2500, ISP2600, ISP8100, ISP8200, and ISP8300 - based host bus adapters do not support FC-IP topology. FL-AL topology is not supported with the ISP2600, ISP8100, ISP8200, and ISP8300-based host bus adapter. Only the ISP2432 supports FC-IP protocol.
